attributes.name: Sudabə Əliyeva
attributes.cv_link: Hello. My name is Sudabe Aliyeva from Azerbaijan. I am interested in the Chat Operator position to work remotely.  I have an Android phone and stable internet. I am confident in online communication and responding to messages promptly. I am ready to work full-time, every day, and I am eager to learn and improve my skills.  Although my English is not fluent, I am able to communicate in written messages and follow instructions carefully. I am highly motivated and reliable.  Thank you for considering my application. I look forward to your reply.
